00:39:32,119 --> 00:39:33,913
If you're curious, come and see.

632
00:39:33,996 --> 00:39:34,872
It seems chaotic.

633
00:39:36,499 --> 00:39:37,625
Yes.

634
00:39:39,001 --> 00:39:40,628
What? It's over?

