636
00:39:43,589 --> 00:39:45,341
Aren't the odds against him now?

637
00:39:45,424 --> 00:39:47,927
Forget the odds, it means he did it.

638
00:39:48,010 --> 00:39:49,637
He wasn't hypoglycemic.

639
00:39:50,930 --> 00:39:52,056
Professor Yang.

640
00:40:09,907 --> 00:40:11,367
Why are you here?

641
00:40:12,201 --> 00:40:13,369
The sugar packet.

642
00:40:15,204 --> 00:40:17,665
-You think I saw it, right?
-Yes.

643
00:40:19,959 --> 00:40:21,836
But why didn't you ask me to testify?

644
00:40:23,629 --> 00:40:26,382
That's your decision,
just as it was for Ye-seul.

645
00:40:33,931 --> 00:40:36,100
My wife got pregnant
