667
00:42:09,735 --> 00:42:12,279
I said I couldn't tell you
to protect my informant.

668
00:42:12,363 --> 00:42:14,365
My father died because of him.

669
00:42:14,448 --> 00:42:15,282
SEO GI-YEOL

670
00:42:15,366 --> 00:42:17,660
