673
00:42:29,296 --> 00:42:30,798
It's Prosecutor Seo Byung-ju.

674
00:42:32,466 --> 00:42:33,551
Seo Byung-ju.

675
00:42:35,052 --> 00:42:36,470
It was you, wasn't it?

676
00:42:37,972 --> 00:42:38,931
That was ages ago.

677
00:42:40,558 --> 00:42:41,976
You should've checked long ago.

678
00:42:42,935 --> 00:42:45,688
Checking the facts is
the basic duty of a judicial officer.

679
00:42:50,401 --> 00:42:53,445
If you want to pass the bar exam at once,
drop the lawsuit

680
00:42:53,529 --> 00:42:54,822
and focus on your studies.

681
00:43:07,960 --> 00:43:09,837
