00:44:08,395 --> 00:44:11,607
-What brings you here?
-Hey, because I missed you.

696
00:44:11,690 --> 00:44:16,070
I'm doing fine thanks to Joon-hwi.
Didn't he tell you?

697
00:44:24,119 --> 00:44:26,455
-Go home.
-Okay.

698
00:44:34,088 --> 00:44:37,716
Dan cut us off ages ago,
and she's not in Korea anymore.

699
00:44:37,800 --> 00:44:39,718
Even if you stayed here--

700
00:44:39,802 --> 00:44:40,719
