701
00:44:41,720 --> 00:44:43,889
I wanted to talk about Prof. Yang's trial.

702
00:44:43,972 --> 00:44:46,433
If she ever calls, I'll let you know.

703
00:44:46,517 --> 00:44:48,519
Didn't she already call you? No?

704
00:44:48,602 --> 00:44:50,145
If she called Prof. Yang,

705
00:44:50,229 --> 00:44:52,981
I'm sure she called her family.

706
00:44:53,065 --> 00:44:54,608
