the number on the tester is wrong.

734
00:46:22,070 --> 00:46:23,697
If we say the date is wrong…

735
00:46:25,657 --> 00:46:27,409
We should just catch the culprit.

736
00:46:30,204 --> 00:46:31,121
Where are we going?

737
00:46:31,830 --> 00:46:33,415
To run an errand for Prof. Kim.

738
00:46:37,628 --> 00:46:39,379
