744
00:46:53,268 --> 00:46:54,478
They all got scared.

745
00:46:55,354 --> 00:46:57,940
The next president,
the man of the Judiciary Committee.

746
00:46:58,023 --> 00:46:59,483
Assemblyman Ko is a big shot.

747
00:46:59,566 --> 00:47:02,861
