764
00:47:53,620 --> 00:47:55,539
I know. I know that.

765
00:47:55,622 --> 00:47:57,499
That's why she didn't defend Prof. Yang.

766
00:48:07,467 --> 00:48:10,387
ASSEMBLYMAN KO HYEONG-SU

