1027
01:02:28,035 --> 01:02:33,624
JEON YE-SEUL'S FIRST TRIAL

1028
01:02:37,170 --> 01:02:38,880
What? They're all his attorneys?

1029
01:02:38,963 --> 01:02:41,132
Why does he have so many?
He must be insane.

1030
01:02:59,984 --> 01:03:01,569
Why isn't Ye-seul's attorney here?

1031
01:03:01,652 --> 01:03:03,988
Her public defender resigned again.

1032
01:03:04,071 --> 01:03:05,406
Then who'll be here?

1033
01:03:05,490 --> 01:03:07,241
I'm sure someone else was assigned.

1034
01:03:07,325 --> 01:03:08,409
All rise.

1035
01:03:23,883 --> 01:03:26,594
GRADES

1036
01:03:31,891 --> 01:03:33,100
DEFENSE COUNSEL, ACCUSED

1037
01:03:38,481 --> 01:03:40,441
PROSECUTION

1038
01:03:45,112 --> 01:03:46,280
Defendant.

1039
01:03:47,156 --> 01:03:48,783
When will your attorney get here?

1040
01:03:53,579 --> 01:03:55,289
They already seem half-hearted.

1041
01:03:56,082 --> 01:03:57,667
She's already in a tight spot.

1042
01:03:58,459 --> 01:04:00,503
-I'll go outside and check.
-Okay.

1043
01:04:14,642 --> 01:04:15,726
I apologize.

1044
01:04:22,233 --> 01:04:23,484
DEFENSE COUNSEL, ACCUSED

1045
01:04:28,447 --> 01:04:30,157
-No way.
-What's going on?

1046
01:04:30,783 --> 01:04:32,076
Prof. Yang is defending her?

1047
01:04:32,952 --> 01:04:33,786
Is that allowed?

1048
01:04:36,956 --> 01:04:38,541
Your Honor.

1049
01:04:38,624 --> 01:04:42,879
In order for the defendant to be
fairly judged by the Court and the people,

1050
01:04:42,962 --> 01:04:46,799
I would like to request a jury trial.

1051
01:05:13,492 --> 01:05:14,702
Ergo,

1052
01:05:14,785 --> 01:05:18,080
I request that Yang Jong-hoon be sentenced
to 20 years in prison.

1053
01:05:18,164 --> 01:05:20,666
So you're deliberately barking up
the wrong tree.

1054
01:05:20,750 --> 01:05:23,252
Make sure you catch the real killer.

1055
01:05:23,336 --> 01:05:25,546
I said I did it alone because of a grudge!

1056
01:05:25,630 --> 01:05:26,797
Something's fishy.

1057
01:05:29,926 --> 01:05:31,218
I need to ask something.

1058
01:05:31,302 --> 01:05:34,138
One of my uncle's belongings is missing.

1059
01:05:34,221 --> 01:05:35,806
-Why?
-Not why but how.

1060
01:05:35,890 --> 01:05:37,433
That's what you want to know.

1061
01:05:37,516 --> 01:05:39,644
You did this to me.
And what? Self-defense?

1062
01:05:39,727 --> 01:05:43,147
The court will be criticized
for appointing a murderer. Not a chance.

1063
01:05:43,230 --> 01:05:44,231
So it's up to you.

1064
01:05:45,066 --> 01:05:46,233
I'll take care of it, sir.

1065
01:05:46,776 --> 01:05:48,194
Professor! What do I do?

1066
01:05:48,277 --> 01:05:52,448
Subtitle translation by Eun Sook Youn
